      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know it says not to, but it was just one glass... like not even a full one. i feel pretty fine, not even buzzed. i just feel like if i take the pill on its own it won't even work because i'm so stressed. wouldnt a tiny bit of alcohol just help the medication kick in maybe??",
